{"tid":477272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣區議員鄒秉恬倡沙灘限奶令","createTime":"2017-11-23T01:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T02:20:51.000Z","uid":6551,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f837a7cafe8dffe2b6be81421292f19e6a89f594","tid":477272,"uid":6551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:38:22.000Z","msg":"最近大台CCTVB出「限奶令」，要一眾女藝人封胸，莫講話市民，有啲藝人都摸不着頭腦，究竟大台搞邊科呀？但原來限奶令不限於大台，最近有區議員都好關注呢個問題。<br />\n話說荃灣區議會下周二（28日）舉行大會，區議員鄒秉恬要求喺當日討論佢嘅限奶令。是咁的，佢畀區會主席封信話，今年荃灣區搞沙灘清潔活動時，發生咗啲令市民同參加者尷尬嘅事，令市民覺得主辦單位派紀念品嗰陣唔公平兼有歧視女性問題。<br />\n於是鄒秉恬就喺區會動議，強烈要求康文署配合荃灣區會嘅活動需要，將來搞沙灘清潔嘅時候，暫時禁止着性感泳衣嘅男女進入沙灘，而活動舉行前15分鐘更加要呼籲、協助啲着比堅尼或G弦泳裝嘅市民離一離場。大家又點睇呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171123/large/a1605a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171123%2Flarge%2Fa1605a.gif&h=8dd16dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171123/20223105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171123%2F20223105&d=zs9%2FH5MOh%2By9Cb8WNyr33U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=125dc7d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171123%2F20223105&h=7e142946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171123/20223105</a>"},{"pid":"3dce67a11afd82c18abde2eb3046555755d2236c","tid":477272,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"佢係死基閪"},{"pid":"c975d94166946aa4b7708910fbb1fc350ef69c4e","tid":477272,"uid":18086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"第一樣應該禁止肥佬參加，影響市容，屌你老母"}]}